title: 820-2850 no video. surprise!?
message:
i've got this 820-2850 with the non surprising no video issue. everything powers powers on and runs but no video on internal or external. i caught the video where pp1v8r was at 1.3v and louis injected 1.8v to make it work again. before i do that i noticed that on diode mode pad 1 of L9560 is .058. pad 2 is .133.

I'm thinking of changing q9560 to see if thats pulling it to ground, but want to check and see if anyone else had some ideas.

title: 820-2850 no video. surprise!?
message: 1.35V there is fine, read the diagram. Does it boot to OSX just without video?
